	('051f9e10-9a82-4901-9747-69b228efd319', 'Summer Camp - S1 Beyond the Book: Mixed Media', 'Dive into the magical world of books in this week’s mixed media art camp! Each day, we will read a beloved story and explore the artistic styles behind them. Inspired by the illustrators’ techniques, campers will create their own imaginative artworks. This camp celebrates creativity, storytelling and the joy of bringing stories to life through art. Camp Specifics: This camp runs from June 1 - 5, 2026 This camp is for ages 6 - 10 DETAILS Morning and afternoon snacks are provided. For all-day camp', '2026-06-01 14:00:00+00', '2026-06-01 21:00:00+00', 'America/Chicago', 'Acadiana Center for the Arts', '101 W Vermilion St, Lafayette, LA', '4d4f7e7d-bb99-46ba-b9c3-de67dd083d3f', 30.2238767, -92.0192319, NULL, NULL, 0.00, true, 'https://acadianacenterforthearts.org/events/summer-camp-beyond-the-book-mixed-media-session-1/?occurrence=2026-06-01', 'Acadiana Center for the Arts', 'bab78b4c-e675-46cc-a2df-0a4406d1ed66', '["https://acadianacenterforthearts.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/Summer-Camp-2026-Graphics_1-Web.jpg"]', 'draft', 0.553, 'ollama', NULL, false, NULL, 0, '''1'':73 ''10'':82 ''101'':100 ''2026'':75 ''5'':74 ''6'':81 ''acadiana'':95 ''afternoon'':86 ''age'':80 ''all-day'':91 ''art'':22,65,99 ''artist'':35 ''artwork'':50 ''behind'':37 ''belov'':30 ''beyond'':4 ''book'':6,15 ''bring'':60 ''camp'':2,23,52,66,69,77,94 ''camper'':44 ''celebr'':53 ''center'':96 ''creat'':46 ''creativ'':54 ''day'':25,93 ''detail'':83 ''dive'':9 ''explor'':33 ''illustr'':42 ''imagin'':49 ''inspir'':39 ''joy'':58 ''june'':72 ''la'':105 ''lafayett'':104 ''life'':63 ''magic'':12 ''media'':8,21 ''mix'':7,20 ''morn'':84 ''provid'':89 ''read'':28 ''run'':70 ''s1'':3 ''snack'':87 ''specif'':67 ''st'':103 ''stori'':31,61 ''storytel'':55 ''style'':36 ''summer'':1 ''techniqu'':43 ''vermilion'':102 ''w'':101 ''week'':18 ''world'':13', '2026-05-21 02:08:36.378111+00', '2026-05-21 19:01:07.249932+00', '{}',